high_descs: Walk straight and turn left just before the sofa to enter into the bedroom, turn right and work then turn left to stand facing the bed.
Pick up the pan lying on the bed.
Turn back then turn left and facing the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, put the pan in it, and close it.
Turn back and walk then turn left and get out of the room, turn left to stand facing the sofa.
Pick up the pan from the sofa.
Turn left turn right to enter into the bedroom then turn right to stand facing against the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, put the pan in it, and close it.
anns.task_desc: Collect all the pan and put them in the cabinet

high_descs: Move across the room and turn left through the bed.
Move toward the bed, and pick up a pan from the mattress.
Holding the tray, turn to the right facing the cabinet.
Put the pan in the cabinet.
Turn to your right and move back through the door, and turn to your left toward the sofa.
Pick up the pan from the sofa.
Move back through the door holding the tray, and turn to the right toward the cabinets.
Place the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Collect pans and place them in the cabinet

high_descs: Walk straight and turn left to reach the bed.
Pick up the pan from the right of the bed.
Turn around to reach the cabinet.
Put the pan in the cabinet.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and turn left to reach the sofa.
Pick up the pan from the left side of the couch.
Turn left to reach the bedroom and turn right to reach the cabinet.
Put the pan in the cabinet next to the other pan.
anns.task_desc: Put two pans in the cabinet.
